727669f.title: Queens: Parsons Boulevard - 15th Avenue
727669f.text:
V
Parsons Boulevard, east side, between 15th and 17th
Avenues, showing Dr. Harrisons Private Sanitarium of 1909.
In 1891 the property was owned by J. P. OtNeill, and in
1873 it was the B. Tatham farm.
P. L. Sperr  April 13, 1927
NO REPRODUCTIONS
